 This little MIDI-Tools send's the <GENERAL MIDI MODE ON> - Message
 to switch any GM-Instrument to GM- (Multi-) Mode automatically.


            **  GM_on   is   F R E E W A R E  **


 It was created to automize the NASTY mode-switching each time my
 @{"KorgĀ05R/W" link "Korg05RW" 0} was switched on ..
 You can place it in your startup-sequence or call it before starting
 your sequencer, MIDI-File-Player, etc.

  GM_on should work fine with any GM-Instrument !!
@endnode

